Package org.forgerock.opendj.maven.doc

Class DocsMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.opendj.maven.doc.DocsMessages
  • public final class DocsMessages
extends Object
    This file contains localizable message descriptors having the resource name org.forgerock.opendj.maven.doc.docs. This file was generated automatically by the i18n-maven-plugin from the property file org/forgerock/opendj/maven/doc/docs.properties and it should not be manually edited.

      • LOG_REF_INTRO

        public static final org.forgerock.i18n.LocalizableMessageDescriptor.Arg0 LOG_REF_INTRO
        xref:../admin-guide/chap-monitoring.adoc#logging["Server Logs"] in the __Administration Guide__ describes logs. Access and audit logs concern client operations rather than OpenDJ directory server and tools, and so are not listed here. Instead, this appendix covers severe and fatal error messages for the directory server and its tools, such as those logged in `/path/to/opendj/logs/errors`, and `/path/to/opendj/logs/replication`.
